<h1 class="list-info__ttl js-list-ttl">Best Mobile Phones Under 40000 (Mar 2022)</h1>
<div class="list-info__dscrptn">
                        Many brands are now offering smartphones with premium experience under the sub - 40K price segment. If you are looking to have a flagship experience, you no need to drop a significant chunk of money (i.e., exceeding Rs 1 lakh). Many of the leading brands like Samsung, Xiaomi, OnePlus, Honor, Motorola, Huawei, Realme, Nokia, Oppo, Vivo, LG, and Sony offer many models under Rs 40,000. These smartphones feature premium design, high-refresh-rate(up to 144Hz) AMOLED display, powerful chipsets from Qualcomm Snapdragon, MediaTek, and HiSilicon Kirin, and faster-charging speeds, offering a flagship-grade experience. Some of the models also include support for 5G network connectivity, higher RAM configurations of up to 12GB, and large battery capacities exceeding 6000 mAh with faster-charging capabilities. The list also includes phones that ace in gaming and photography with features like liquid cooling, optical zoom, etc. Without any further ado, let   s dive into the wide array of products, present on the website, and you would surely fall in love with them! The price list of best mobiles under Rs 40,000 at MySmartPrice is updated quite often so you can find all the latest releases. We have also provided you with the comparison table to match the specs and check what it brings to the table. The mobiles in the list also include expert scores that further assist you in making the right purchase decisions.     function checkSponsoredFrequency() {
        var spons = document.getElementById('sponsor_counts');
        if(spons){
            var imp = spons.getAttribute('data-imp');
            var frequency = spons.getAttribute('data-frequency');
            var camp_id = spons.getAttribute('data-campaign');
            var mspid = spons.getAttribute('data-mspid');
            var ga_impression = spons.getAttribute('data-impression');
            var category = spons.getAttribute('data-category');
            var ga_cat = 'web:'+category;
            window.ga && ga('send', 'event', ga_cat, ga_impression, 'sponsored',{ nonInteraction: true });
            if(imp === '0'){
            var cookie_name = getCookie('camp_frequency'+camp_id);
            if (frequency === '0') {
                    spons.style.display = 'block';
            } else {
                if(cookie_name <= frequency){
                    spons.style.display = 'block';
                }else {
                    document.getElementById('prd_'+mspid).style.display = 'block';
                }
            }
            if (cookie_name !== '') {
                cookie_name++;
                document.cookie = 'camp_frequency'+camp_id+'='+cookie_name+'; expires=0; path=/';
            }else{
                document.cookie = 'camp_frequency'+camp_id+'=1; expires=0; path=/';
            }
            }
        }
    }
    
    function getCookie(cname) {
        var name = cname + '=';
        var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
        for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
            var c = ca[i];
            while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') c = c.substring(1);
            if (c.indexOf(name) != -1) return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
        }
        return '';
    }
    checkSponsoredFrequency();
